# Anonymous sub
topic read $SYS/#
topic read builders/#
topic read jobs/+
topic read tasks/#
topic read cancel/#

# Builder pub/sub - copy for each builder
user arch/name
topic readwrite builders/arch/name
topic readwrite tasks/arch/name/+
topic readwrite jobs/+
topic read cancel/#

# IRC pub/sub
user irc
topic read builders/#
topic read jobs/+
topic read tasks/#
topic readwrite cancel/#

# enqueue pub/sub
user enqueue
topic readwrite builders/#
topic readwrite jobs/+
topic readwrite tasks/#
topic readwrite cancel/#

# All clients
pattern write $SYS/broker/connection/%c/state
